description: Provides feedback against the specified assistant for the specified target. This API only supports generative targets.

parameters.name: assistantId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q in Connect assistant.

parameters.name: targetId
parameters.description: The identifier of the feedback target.

parameters.name: targetType
parameters.description: The type of the feedback target.

parameters.name: contentFeedback
parameters.description: Information about the feedback provided. generativeContentFeedbackData (dict) --- Information about the feedback for a generative target type. The relevance of the feedback.

nested_params.name: generativeContentFeedbackData
nested_params.description: Information about the feedback for a generative target type.
